text: Durango to San Luis Potosi – 6 days, 313 miles Thursday, January 26th, 2006 In the past week, I have cut across the high central plateau of Mexico.
According to a doctor I stayed with in the town of Fresnillo (met him on the street while asking directions to the firehouse), the area is the world’s second largest producer of silver.
